Package: dng
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2017-11-22
Title: Distributions and Gradients
Type: Package
Author: Feng Li, Jiayue Zeng
Maintainer: Jiayue Zeng <zengjiayue@126.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Description: Provides density, distribution function, quantile function and random generation for the split normal and split-t distributions, and computes the mean, variance, skewness and kurtosis for the split normal andsplit-t distribution (Li, F, Villani, M. and Kohn, R. (2010) <doi:10.1016/j.jspi.2010.04.031>).
